incrementToolWidth.desc: Increment the brush or eraser tool width, whichever is selected.
incrementToolWidth.title: Increment Tool Width

prevEntity.title: Prev Layer
prevEntity.desc: Select the previous layer in the list.

filterSelected.title: Filter
filterSelected.desc: Filter the selected layer. Only applies to Raster and Control layers.

resetSelected.title: Reset Layer
resetSelected.desc: Reset the selected layer. Only applies to Inpaint Mask and Regional Guidance.

nextEntity.title: Next Layer
nextEntity.desc: Select the next layer in the list.

setFillToWhite.title: Set Color to White
setFillToWhite.desc: Set the current tool color to white.

applyFilter.title: Apply Filter
applyFilter.desc: Apply the pending filter to the selected layer.

applyTransform.desc: Apply the pending transform to the selected layer.
applyTransform.title: Apply Transform

fitLayersToCanvas.desc: Scale and position the view to fit all visible layers.
fitLayersToCanvas.title: Fit Layers to Canvas

decrementToolWidth.title: Decrement Tool Width
decrementToolWidth.desc: Decrement the brush or eraser tool width, whichever is selected.

quickSwitch.title: Layer Quick Switch
quickSwitch.desc: Switch between the last two selected layers. If a layer is bookmarked, always switch between it and the last non-bookmarked layer.

fitBboxToCanvas.title: Fit Bbox to Canvas
fitBboxToCanvas.desc: Scale and position the view to fit the bbox.

pasteSelectionWithEdges.title: Paste with Edges
pasteSelectionWithEdges.desc: Paste copied nodes, edges, and all edges connected to copied nodes.

recallSeed.title: Recall Seed
recallSeed.desc: Recall the seed for the current image.

recallPrompts.desc: Recall the positive and negative prompts for the current image.
recallPrompts.title: Recall Prompts

remix.title: Remix
remix.desc: Recall all metadata except for the seed for the current image.

useSize.desc: Use the current image's size as the bbox size.
useSize.title: Use Size

runPostprocessing.title: Run Postprocessing
runPostprocessing.desc: Run the selected postprocessing on the current image.

toggleMetadata.title: Show/Hide Metadata
toggleMetadata.desc: Show or hide the current image's metadata overlay.

galleryNavRightAlt.desc: Same as Navigate Right, but selects the compare image, opening compare mode if it isn't already open.
galleryNavRightAlt.title: Navigate Right (Compare Image)

galleryNavRight.desc: Navigate right in the gallery grid, selecting that image. If at the last image of the row, go to the next row. If at the last image of the page, go to the next page.
galleryNavRight.title: Navigate Right

galleryNavUp.desc: Navigate up in the gallery grid, selecting that image. If at the top of the page, go to the previous page.
galleryNavUp.title: Navigate Up

galleryNavDown.title: Navigate Down
galleryNavDown.desc: Navigate down in the gallery grid, selecting that image. If at the bottom of the page, go to the next page.

galleryNavLeft.title: Navigate Left
galleryNavLeft.desc: Navigate left in the gallery grid, selecting that image. If at the first image of the row, go to the previous row. If at the first image of the page, go to the previous page.

galleryNavDownAlt.title: Navigate Down (Compare Image)
galleryNavDownAlt.desc: Same as Navigate Down, but selects the compare image, opening compare mode if it isn't already open.

galleryNavLeftAlt.desc: Same as Navigate Left, but selects the compare image, opening compare mode if it isn't already open.
galleryNavLeftAlt.title: Navigate Left (Compare Image)

clearSelection.desc: Clear the current selection, if any.
clearSelection.title: Clear Selection

deleteSelection.title: Delete
deleteSelection.desc: Delete all selected images. By default, you will be prompted to confirm deletion. If the images are currently in use in the app, you will be warned.

galleryNavUpAlt.title: Navigate Up (Compare Image)
galleryNavUpAlt.desc: Same as Navigate Up, but selects the compare image, opening compare mode if it isn't already open.

selectAllOnPage.title: Select All On Page
selectAllOnPage.desc: Select all images on the current page.
